      {
        "text": "### Loops and Rests\n\nYou can combine nested loops and rests to create special moments that only happen once in a while\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/a49bb0ffaeb146dd279396aef4f816cb-loop-rest-2.png",
