        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Loops and Rests\n\nYou can combine loops and rests to make offbeat patterns, like this clap beat.\n\nOffbeat patterns are common in some musical styles like Reggaeton.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/72d5f0f0bc45a3445bd04dc14121e3c5-loop-rest-3.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-loops-practice-panel-offbeat-8239ddc0-a4c8-408b-89b0-fb8b7f6b7b22",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Loops and Rests\n\nYou can combine nested loops and rests to repeat these patterns over the vocals of a song\n",
